# SECTION 17: MEMORY TRICKS

## 17.1 Mnemonics for JCF

```
COLLECTION TYPES:
"List Saves Data"  → List = Sequential, Duplicate allowed
"Set Stands Unique"→ Set = No Duplicates
"Queue Forms Lines"→ Queue = FIFO (First come, first served)
"Stack Plates Up"  → Stack = LIFO (Last plate = first used)

MAP TYPES:
"H for Hash = HASH-y (fast but messy)"     → HashMap = Fast, no order
"L for Linked = LINKS in order"            → LinkedHashMap = Ordered
"T for Tree = TREE-sorted"                 → TreeMap = Sorted

SET TYPES:
"Hash = Haphazard"      → HashSet = No order
"Linked = Lined up"     → LinkedHashSet = Insertion order
"Tree = Tall & Sorted"  → TreeSet = Sorted
```

## 17.2 Quick Reference Tricks

